# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Cross-check: all three dunders absent from all four classes
#
# Consolidating the negative results to confirm no concurrent.futures class
# defines any of the three wave-622 dunders in its own __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

